      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            By downloading, accessing, or using the Clover mobile application (the "App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you disagree with any part of these Terms, you may not access or use the App. These Terms apply to all users of the App on iOS and Android devices.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 mt-8">Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            Clover is a mobile application that helps parents and caregivers locate baby changing facilities, family restrooms, high chairs, and nursing rooms. The App provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>An interactive map showing nearby baby-friendly facilities</li>
            <li>The ability to search for specific locations</li>
            <li>Community-contributed information including photos and reviews</li>
            <li>The ability to contribute new places and photos to help other users</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 mt-8">Eligibility</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            You must be at least 13 years old (or 16 in the European Economic Area) to use this App. By using the App, you represent and warrant that you meet this age requirement. The App is intended for parents, caregivers, and individuals seeking baby-friendly facilities.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 mt-8">Use of Service</h2>
          
