          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            You agree to use Clover only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Submit false, misleading, or inaccurate information about facilities</li>
            <li>Upload inappropriate, offensive, illegal, or sexually explicit content</li>
            <li>Upload photos containing identifiable children without proper consent</li>
            <li>Harass, abuse, threaten, or harm other users</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or networks</li>
            <li>Use automated tools, bots, or scripts to scrape or collect data</li>
            <li>Interfere with, disrupt, or impose an unreasonable burden on the service</li>
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Impersonate any person or entity</li>
            <li>Use the App for commercial purposes without our permission</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Location Services</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            The App requires location permissions to function properly. You may grant or deny location access at any time through your device settings. Without location access, some features of the App may not work as intended.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Device Permissions</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            The App may request the following permissions:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> To display your position on the map and show nearby facilities</li>
            <li><strong>Camera:</strong> To take photos of facilities (optional)</li>
            <li><strong>Photo Library:</strong> To select and upload photos (optional)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            You can manage these permissions at any time in your device settings.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 mt-8">User Contributions</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Types of Contributions</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            You may contribute to the App by:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Adding new baby-friendly facilities</li>
            <li>Uploading photos of facilities</li>
            <li>Providing feedback on existing facilities</li>
            <li>Reporting incorrect or outdated information</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Content Ownership and License</h3>
