          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            This license allows us to make your contributions available to other App users to help them find baby-friendly facilities.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Content Guidelines</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            All user contributions must:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Be accurate and truthful to the best of your knowledge</li>
            <li>Not contain personal information of others (names, addresses, phone numbers)</li>
            <li>Not include copyrighted material you don't have permission to use</li>
            <li>Be appropriate for a family-friendly, all-ages service</li>
            <li>Not contain identifiable photos of children without proper consent</li>
            <li>Not promote commercial products, services, or businesses</li>
            <li>Not contain spam, advertising, or solicitation</li>
            <li>Be relevant to baby-changing facilities and related amenities</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            By uploading photos, you represent that you have the right to share them and that they do not violate any third-party rights.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Content Moderation</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
            We reserve the right to review, remove, or modify any user contributions that violate these Terms or our community guidelines, with or without notice. Repeated violations may result in account suspension, termination, or permanent ban from the service.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 mt-8">Reporting and Moderation</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            Users can report places for incorrect information, closure, inappropriate content, or other issues. When you report a place:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>The place may be immediately hidden from your map view</li>
            <li>Reports are sent to our moderation team for review</li>
            <li>We may contact you for additional information</li>
            <li>Abuse of the reporting system may result in account restrictions</li>
            <li>False or malicious reports may lead to account termination</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 mt-8">Data Sources and Accuracy</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            Clover aggregates data from various sources including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>The Great British Public Toilet Map (GBPTM)</li>
            <li>OpenStreetMap (OSM)</li>
            <li>User contributions</li>
            <li>Publicly available datasets</li>
